Reflex.SayString: Hi! I'm Mad Scientist Mark!
MY ZOMBIES ARE GOING TO EAT YOU!

Doh! I dropped another potion! There goes another one! Don't drink those potions! They'll, err, make you sick! OMG I wish I had hands, then I wouldn't drop these. Grrrrrr.....I should try not to these potions, shouldn't I?
OH NOES! I dropped a bomb! Don't touch that bomb! You'll blow up! That bomb is highly implosive, don't touch it! TEHEHEHEHEHE! THE BOMB GOES BOOM!
Ack! I dropped some more coins! Don't pick my coins up, that would be stealing! NOOO! I need those coins to buy a new toupé! Stay away from my coins!
Gah I dropped another heart! Don't eat those hearts! They'll poison you! THESE HEARTS ARE TOO SLIPPERY! Get away from those hearts! I need them! DON'T EAT MY LUNCH..I mean...my hearts!
MWUAHAAHAHAHAHA! l0l u rt3h n00bzzz MY ZOMBIES ARE EATING YOU! Hurry up and die! Wow, you really do suck at this. Look! It bit you! HAH! That's cheating! Stop taking my stuff!

-Left 4 Kodu Classic- By El Bishi v1.0
Mad Scientist Mark is tryng to feed you to his Zombies! Survive for as long as you can! ____________________
-Characters- Red <flyfish> = Player 1 Green <flyfish> = Player 2 Blue <flyfish> = Player 3 Yellow <flyfish> = Player 4 <sputnik><sputnik><sputnik> = Zombies! Flying <Kodu> = Mad Scientist Mark ____________________
-Controls- <a> = Spawn/Respawn when prompted (when you die, you must wait 5 seconds before being able to respawn) <ls> = Move <rt> = Shoot <y> = Show Instructions (Player 1 only) ____________________
-Powerups- Mad Scientist Mark will fly around, complain, and randomly drop powerups. These will disappear after 15 seconds if not picked up.
Gold <Coin> = +10 points Red <heart> = +50% health Purple <Ammo> = Decimates <sputnik>s on the map Green <wisp> = For 10 seconds, any <sputnik> that bites you will violently implode Blue <wisp> = 10 seconds of super speed White <wisp> = 10 seconds of invincibility ____________________
-Scores- White = Total amount of <sputnik> kills from all players Grey = Total amount of seconds since the first player spawned Purple = Current Difficulty Red = Player 1's current amount of points Green = Player 2's current amount of points Blue = Player 3's current amount of points Yellow = Player 4's current amount of points ____________________
-Point System- Each <sputnik> killed (not including Green <wisp> or Purple <ammo> kills) = +1 point Each Gold <coin> picked up = +10 points Death = -100 points ____________________
-Difficulty System- Every 25 <sputnik>s that are killed = +1 difficulty Every 30 seconds that any player is alive = +1 difficulty Every player that spawns = +5 difficulty (only for initial spawn)
For every 5 difficulty points, a <sputnik> will spawn every second. After 200, the amount of <sputnik>s that spawn each second will no longer change. ____________________
-Respawning- When you die, your tree (the same colour as your fish) will glow white and make a siren noise for 5 seconds.
If you have less than 0 points, it's game over for you, and you will be unable to respawn.
After 5 seconds, you will hear a beep, your tree will glow your colou an display a prompt telling you that you are able to respawn by pressing <a>. ____________________
-Loosing Conditions- The game ends when all players are dead at the same time as all players having less than 0 points.
Oh and you are unable to win. If you manage to win, have this: <coin> ____________________
-Cheats- Yeah, there's cheats. Only Player 1 can use them, and they might break everything... <lt> + <b> = Increase Difficulty <lt> + <x> = Decrease Difficulty ____________________
That's all!
Remember, Player 1 can press <y> at any time if you wish to see the instructions again.
If you have any feedback, I'd love to hear it. My gamertag is El Bishi.
Thanks, have fun, an good luck! :)
